General.Name: WAWEL SA
General.Description: Wawel S.A. produces and sells cocoa, chocolate, and confectionary products in Poland. It offers a range of chocolate bars, cocoas plums, vanilla souffles, chocolate pastilles, chocolate coated candies, fresh and fruity jellies, dragon gummies, tofflairs, cream fudges, caramels, choco mints, and cocoa products. The company sells its products to retail and discount chains. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 1898 and is headquartered in Kraków, Poland. Wawel S.A. is a subsidiary of Hosta International AG.
